snippet.title: Tokyo Highway Battle Trailer 1996
snippet.description:
Tokyo Highway Battle Trailer 1996

Official Content From Jaleco

Race thru the Japanese metropolis in a 454 horse power racing machine. You can customize your racer with turbo chargers, dual exhausts, wide tires and more. Twelve world class sports cars to choose from.
Platforms: Sony PlayStation

Sony PlayStation
